        "content": "<p>badeend requested <a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/bytecodealliance/teams/wasmtime-wasi-reviewers\">wasmtime-wasi-reviewers</a> for a review on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12834\">PR #12834</a>.</p>",
